WEBVTT

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Zhang Peisan: Yes — that day I was returning from exercising my horse when I saw Xuechun alone in the outskirts, and I was seized by an evil impulse…

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:34.000
Official: And then?

00:00:35.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Zhang Peisan: I — I killed her. My hand was stained with blood, and when I fled I left behind the crimson palm print.

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:17.000
Wang Qianjin: Did you all hear that? This is the murderer's own confession!

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:38.000
Official: Zhang Peisan, you have committed the crime of murder. According to the law, you shall be beheaded!

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:52.000
Zhang Peisan: Spare my life, Your Honor, spare my life!

00:01:53.000 --> 00:02:05.000
Official: Guards, take Zhang Peisan away!

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:22.000
Wang Qianjin: Lin Zhaode is innocent — please restore his good name, Your Honor!

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:26.000
Official: Lin Zhaode is innocent and shall be released!
